   1:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp **** /**
   2:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * mpr121_calibrate.cpp â€” Full sensor calibration for GaletSynth
   3:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * Daisy Seed â€” Bit-Bang I2C  SDA=D12  SCL=D11
   4:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *
   5:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * Phase 1a  CDC Ă— CDT sweep (9 configs)
   6:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *           Find the best charge current / charge time for the sensor.
   7:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * Phase 1b  FFI Ă— ESI sweep (12 configs, best CDC/CDT locked)
   8:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *           Fine-tune filter iterations and sample interval.
   9:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * Phase 2   Two guided swipe rounds: LIGHT (â†’ PRESSURE_MIN_REF) and
  10:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *           HARD (â†’ PRESSURE_MAX_REF), 8 s each. TOUCH_THRESHOLD = 10.
  11:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *
  12:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * At the end, prints the exact lines to paste into src/main.cpp.
  13:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *
  14:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  * Build:
  15:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *   make TARGET=tools/mpr121_calibrate libdaisy_dir=<path> \
  16:tools/mpr121_calibrate.cpp ****  *        SYSTEM_FILES_DIR=<path>/core LIBDAISY_DIR=<path>
