  12:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now only Normal Mode is supported,
  13:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** Sample and hold mode provides reduced power consumption, but requires a bit more setup.
  14:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
  15:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now connecting the DAC through other internal peripherals is also not supported.
  16:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
